headline: Did Katz’s Deli Choosing Square Just Strengthen Block’s (SQ) Omnichannel Growth Story?
summary: Square recently announced that Katz’s Delicatessen, a historic New York institution, has adopted Square's comprehensive commerce platform to power operations across two locations and nationwide shipping. This collaboration allows Katz’s to handle both high-volume in-store orders and robust e-commerce expansion, highlighting Square’s capabilities in supporting iconic businesses through omnichannel solutions.
